{
  "stem": "24195.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was only maybe for a month.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I hadn't even-- and I had registered with the employment office again, but I had not done anything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they hadn't called me, so then my-- then we got really worried that we did not go to the Gestapo hearing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that whatever it is, that by not-- by not showing up there may make things worse.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we decided tomorrow we're going to go to the Gestapo headquarters, which was notorious for once people enter that building-- it's the big headquarters.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the national headquarters for all the Gestapo activities in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Once they entered, most of the people don't ever come out again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that-- that had that reputation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So what we decided, the next day, we're going to go there, my mother and I, take that summons with us and say, we had a family emergency.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We couldn't make it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we're coming now and trying to clarify, to clear up this case.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we go there, and it happens to be July 20, 1944.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's the day that the-- a group of high ranking army officers, German army officers, assassinate Hitler, planting a bomb in a briefcase in his Wolf's Lair headquarters outside Berlin.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And but the bomb goes off, but Hitler has just either walked out of the room or to the other end of the room.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somebody else gets killed, but Hitler doesn't get killed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, that defeats the whole-- the whole plot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nothing is-- we didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're coming in, go into the headquarters, reporting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You go in through guards, check in through the guards, show them the summons, go upstairs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He says-- every, every door has-- it's like a prison here, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
